casebody.data:
Clark P. Washburn, et al., Appellants, v. Katherine Schmuck, Respondent. Decided May 3, 1886. Appeal from judgment entered upon verdict, and from order denying motion for new trial. G. W. Galinger, for appellants. John Hardy, for respondent.

Before Sedgwick, Ch. J., and Freedman, J.

Opinion

Per Curiam.

Judgment and order affirmed, with costs.
